{"data":[{"name":"56:1","price":"当那件大事发生的时候，","arabic":"إِذَا وَقَعَتِ ٱلۡوَاقِعَةُ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":4980,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"56:2","price":"没有任何人否认其发生。","arabic":"لَيۡسَ لِوَقۡعَتِهَا كَاذِبَةٌ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":4981,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"56:3","price":"那件大事将是能使人降级，能使人升级的；","arabic":"خَافِضَةٞ رَّافِعَةٌ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":4982,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"56:4","price":"当大地震荡，","arabic":"إِذَا رُجَّتِ ٱلۡأَرۡضُ رَجّٗا","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":4983,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"56:5","price":"山峦粉碎，","arabic":"وَبُسَّتِ ٱلۡجِبَالُ بَسّٗا","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":4984,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"56:6","price":"化为散漫的尘埃，","arabic":"فَكَانَتۡ هَبَآءٗ مُّنۢبَثّٗا","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":4985,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"56:7","price":"而你们分为三等的时候。","arabic":"وَكُنتُمۡ أَزۡوَٰجٗا ثَلَٰثَةٗ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":4986,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"56:8","price":"幸福者，幸福者是何等的人？","arabic":"فَأَصۡحَٰبُ ٱلۡمَيۡمَنَةِ مَآ أَصۡحَٰبُ ٱلۡمَيۡمَنَةِ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":4987,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"56:9","price":"薄命者，薄命者是何等的人？","arabic":"وَأَصۡحَٰبُ ٱلۡمَشۡـَٔمَةِ مَآ أَصۡحَٰبُ ٱلۡمَشۡـَٔمَةِ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":4988,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"56:10","price":"最先行善者，是最先入乐园的人，","arabic":"وَٱلسَّٰبِقُونَ ٱلسَّٰبِقُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":4989,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"56:11","price":"这等人，确是蒙主眷顾的。","arabic":"أُوْلَٰٓئِكَ ٱلۡمُقَرَّبُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":4990,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"56:12","price":"他们在恩泽的乐园中。","arabic":"فِي جَنَّٰتِ ٱلنَّعِيمِ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":4991,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"56:13","price":"许多前人","arabic":"ثُلَّةٞ مِّنَ ٱلۡأَوَّلِينَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":4992,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"56:14","price":"和少数后人，","arabic":"وَقَلِيلٞ مِّنَ ٱلۡأٓخِرِينَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":4993,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"56:15","price":"在珠宝镶成的床榻上，","arabic":"عَلَىٰ سُرُرٖ مَّوۡضُونَةٖ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":4994,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"56:16","price":"彼此相对地靠在上面。","arabic":"مُّتَّكِـِٔينَ عَلَيۡهَا مُتَقَٰبِلِينَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":4995,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"56:17","price":"长生不老的僮仆，轮流着服待他们，","arabic":"يَطُوفُ عَلَيۡهِمۡ وِلۡدَٰنٞ مُّخَلَّدُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":4996,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"56:18","price":"捧着盏和壶，与满杯的醴泉；","arabic":"بِأَكۡوَابٖ وَأَبَارِيقَ وَكَأۡسٖ مِّن مَّعِينٖ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":4997,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"56:19","price":"他们不因那醴泉而头痛，也不酩酊。","arabic":"لَّا يُصَدَّعُونَ عَنۡهَا وَلَا يُنزِفُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":4998,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"56:20","price":"他们有自己所选择的水果，","arabic":"وَفَٰكِهَةٖ مِّمَّا يَتَخَيَّرُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":4999,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"56:21","price":"和自己所爱好的鸟肉。","arabic":"وَلَحۡمِ طَيۡرٖ مِّمَّا يَشۡتَهُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5000,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"56:22","price":"还有白皙的、美目的妻子，","arabic":"وَحُورٌ عِينٞ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5001,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"56:23","price":"好像藏在蚌壳里的珍珠一样。","arabic":"كَأَمۡثَٰلِ ٱللُّؤۡلُوِٕ ٱلۡمَكۡنُونِ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5002,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"56:24","price":"那是为了报酬他们的善行。","arabic":"جَزَآءَۢ بِمَا كَانُواْ يَعۡمَلُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5003,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"56:25","price":"他们在乐园里，听不到恶言和谎话，","arabic":"لَا يَسۡمَعُونَ فِيهَا لَغۡوٗا وَلَا تَأۡثِيمًا","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5004,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"56:26","price":"但听到说：祝你们平安！祝你们平安！","arabic":"إِلَّا قِيلٗا سَلَٰمٗا سَلَٰمٗا","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5005,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"56:27","price":"幸福者，幸福者是何等的人？","arabic":"وَأَصۡحَٰبُ ٱلۡيَمِينِ مَآ أَصۡحَٰبُ ٱلۡيَمِينِ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5006,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"56:28","price":"他们享受无刺的酸枣树，","arabic":"فِي سِدۡرٖ مَّخۡضُودٖ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5007,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"56:29","price":"结实累累的（香蕉）树；","arabic":"وَطَلۡحٖ مَّنضُودٖ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5008,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"56:30","price":"漫漫的树荫；","arabic":"وَظِلّٖ مَّمۡدُودٖ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5009,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"56:31","price":"泛泛的流水；","arabic":"وَمَآءٖ مَّسۡكُوبٖ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5010,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"56:32","price":"丰富的水果，","arabic":"وَفَٰكِهَةٖ كَثِيرَةٖ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5011,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"56:33","price":"四时不绝，可以随意摘食；","arabic":"لَّا مَقۡطُوعَةٖ وَلَا مَمۡنُوعَةٖ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5012,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"56:34","price":"与被升起的床榻。","arabic":"وَفُرُشٖ مَّرۡفُوعَةٍ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5013,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"56:35","price":"我使她们重新生长，","arabic":"إِنَّآ أَنشَأۡنَٰهُنَّ إِنشَآءٗ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5014,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"56:36","price":"我使她们常为处女，","arabic":"فَجَعَلۡنَٰهُنَّ أَبۡكَارًا","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5015,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"56:37","price":"依恋丈夫，彼此同岁；","arabic":"عُرُبًا أَتۡرَابٗا","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5016,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"56:38","price":"这些都是幸福者所享受的。","arabic":"لِّأَصۡحَٰبِ ٱلۡيَمِينِ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5017,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"56:39","price":"许多前人","arabic":"ثُلَّةٞ مِّنَ ٱلۡأَوَّلِينَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5018,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"56:40","price":"和许多后人。","arabic":"وَثُلَّةٞ مِّنَ ٱلۡأٓخِرِينَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5019,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"56:41","price":"薄命者，薄命者是何等的人？","arabic":"وَأَصۡحَٰبُ ٱلشِّمَالِ مَآ أَصۡحَٰبُ ٱلشِّمَالِ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5020,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"56:42","price":"他们在毒风和沸水中，","arabic":"فِي سَمُومٖ وَحَمِيمٖ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5021,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"56:43","price":"在黑烟的阴影下，","arabic":"وَظِلّٖ مِّن يَحۡمُومٖ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5022,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"56:44","price":"既不凉爽，又不美观。","arabic":"لَّا بَارِدٖ وَلَا كَرِيمٍ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5023,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"56:45","price":"以前他们确是奢侈的，","arabic":"إِنَّهُمۡ كَانُواْ قَبۡلَ ذَٰلِكَ مُتۡرَفِينَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5024,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"56:46","price":"确是固执大罪的，","arabic":"وَكَانُواْ يُصِرُّونَ عَلَى ٱلۡحِنثِ ٱلۡعَظِيمِ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5025,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"56:47","price":"他们常说：“难道我们死后，已变成尘土和枯骨的时候，我们必定要复活吗？ ”","arabic":"وَكَانُواْ يَقُولُونَ أَئِذَا مِتۡنَا وَكُنَّا تُرَابٗا وَعِظَٰمًا أَءِنَّا لَمَبۡعُوثُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5026,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"56:48","price":"连我们的祖先，也要复活吗？”","arabic":"أَوَءَابَآؤُنَا ٱلۡأَوَّلُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5027,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"56:49","price":"你说：前人和后人，","arabic":"قُلۡ إِنَّ ٱلۡأَوَّلِينَ وَٱلۡأٓخِرِينَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5028,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"56:50","price":"在一个著名的日期和特定时间必定要被集合。","arabic":"لَمَجۡمُوعُونَ إِلَىٰ مِيقَٰتِ يَوۡمٖ مَّعۡلُومٖ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5029,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"56:51","price":"然后迷误的、否认复活的人们啊！","arabic":"ثُمَّ إِنَّكُمۡ أَيُّهَا ٱلضَّآلُّونَ ٱلۡمُكَذِّبُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5030,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"56:52","price":"你们必定食攒楛木的果实，","arabic":"لَأٓكِلُونَ مِن شَجَرٖ مِّن زَقُّومٖ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5031,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"56:53","price":"而以它充饥，","arabic":"فَمَالِـُٔونَ مِنۡهَا ٱلۡبُطُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5032,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"56:54","price":"然后痛饮沸水，","arabic":"فَشَٰرِبُونَ عَلَيۡهِ مِنَ ٱلۡحَمِيمِ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5033,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"56:55","price":"像害消渴病的骆驼饮凉水一样。","arabic":"فَشَٰرِبُونَ شُرۡبَ ٱلۡهِيمِ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5034,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"56:56","price":"这是他们在报应之日所受的款待。","arabic":"هَٰذَا نُزُلُهُمۡ يَوۡمَ ٱلدِّينِ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5035,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"56:57","price":"我曾创造你们，你们怎不信复活呢？","arabic":"نَحۡنُ خَلَقۡنَٰكُمۡ فَلَوۡلَا تُصَدِّقُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5036,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"56:58","price":"你们告诉我吧！你们所射的精液，","arabic":"أَفَرَءَيۡتُم مَّا تُمۡنُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5037,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"56:59","price":"究竟是你们把它造成人呢？还是我把它造成人呢？","arabic":"ءَأَنتُمۡ تَخۡلُقُونَهُۥٓ أَمۡ نَحۡنُ ٱلۡخَٰلِقُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5038,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"56:60","price":"我曾将死亡分配给你们，任何人不能阻挠我，","arabic":"نَحۡنُ قَدَّرۡنَا بَيۡنَكُمُ ٱلۡمَوۡتَ وَمَا نَحۡنُ بِمَسۡبُوقِينَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5039,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"56:61","price":"不让我改变你们的品性，而使你们生长在你们所不知的状态中。","arabic":"عَلَىٰٓ أَن نُّبَدِّلَ أَمۡثَٰلَكُمۡ وَنُنشِئَكُمۡ فِي مَا لَا تَعۡلَمُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5040,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"56:62","price":"你们确已知道初次的生长，你们怎不觉悟呢？","arabic":"وَلَقَدۡ عَلِمۡتُمُ ٱلنَّشۡأَةَ ٱلۡأُولَىٰ فَلَوۡلَا تَذَكَّرُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5041,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"56:63","price":"你们告诉我吧！你们所耕种的庄稼，","arabic":"أَفَرَءَيۡتُم مَّا تَحۡرُثُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5042,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"56:64","price":"究竟是你们使它发荣呢？还是我使它发荣呢？","arabic":"ءَأَنتُمۡ تَزۡرَعُونَهُۥٓ أَمۡ نَحۡنُ ٱلزَّٰرِعُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5043,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"56:65","price":"假若我意欲，我必使它凋零，而你们变成诧异者，","arabic":"لَوۡ نَشَآءُ لَجَعَلۡنَٰهُ حُطَٰمٗا فَظَلۡتُمۡ تَفَكَّهُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5044,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"56:66","price":"你们将说：“我们是遭损失的。”","arabic":"إِنَّا لَمُغۡرَمُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5045,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"56:67","price":"不然，我们是被剥夺的。”","arabic":"بَلۡ نَحۡنُ مَحۡرُومُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5046,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"56:68","price":"你们告诉吧！你们所饮的水，","arabic":"أَفَرَءَيۡتُمُ ٱلۡمَآءَ ٱلَّذِي تَشۡرَبُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5047,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"56:69","price":"究竟是你们使它从云上降下的呢？还是我使它降下的呢？","arabic":"ءَأَنتُمۡ أَنزَلۡتُمُوهُ مِنَ ٱلۡمُزۡنِ أَمۡ نَحۡنُ ٱلۡمُنزِلُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5048,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"56:70","price":"假若我意欲，我必使它变成苦的，你们怎么不感谢呢？","arabic":"لَوۡ نَشَآءُ جَعَلۡنَٰهُ أُجَاجٗا فَلَوۡلَا تَشۡكُرُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5049,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"56:71","price":"你们告诉吧！你们所钻取的火；","arabic":"أَفَرَءَيۡتُمُ ٱلنَّارَ ٱلَّتِي تُورُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5050,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"56:72","price":"究竟是你们使燧木生长的呢？还是我使它生长的呢？","arabic":"ءَأَنتُمۡ أَنشَأۡتُمۡ شَجَرَتَهَآ أَمۡ نَحۡنُ ٱلۡمُنشِـُٔونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5051,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"56:73","price":"我以它为教训，并且以它为荒野的居民的慰藉，","arabic":"نَحۡنُ جَعَلۡنَٰهَا تَذۡكِرَةٗ وَمَتَٰعٗا لِّلۡمُقۡوِينَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5052,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"56:74","price":"故你应当颂扬你的主的大名。","arabic":"فَسَبِّحۡ بِٱسۡمِ رَبِّكَ ٱلۡعَظِيمِ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5053,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"56:75","price":"我必以星宿的没落处盟誓，","arabic":"۞ فَلَآ أُقۡسِمُ بِمَوَٰقِعِ ٱلنُّجُومِ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5054,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"56:76","price":"这确是一个重大的盟誓，假若你们知道。","arabic":"وَإِنَّهُۥ لَقَسَمٞ لَّوۡ تَعۡلَمُونَ عَظِيمٌ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5055,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"56:77","price":"这确是宝贵的《古兰经》，","arabic":"إِنَّهُۥ لَقُرۡءَانٞ كَرِيمٞ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5056,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"56:78","price":"记录在珍藏的经本中，","arabic":"فِي كِتَٰبٖ مَّكۡنُونٖ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5057,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"56:79","price":"只有纯洁者才得抚摸那经本。","arabic":"لَّا يَمَسُّهُۥٓ إِلَّا ٱلۡمُطَهَّرُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5058,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"56:80","price":"《古兰经》是从全世界的主降示的。","arabic":"تَنزِيلٞ مِّن رَّبِّ ٱلۡعَٰلَمِينَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5059,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"56:81","price":"难道你们藐视这训辞，","arabic":"أَفَبِهَٰذَا ٱلۡحَدِيثِ أَنتُم مُّدۡهِنُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5060,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"56:82","price":"而以否认代替感谢吗？","arabic":"وَتَجۡعَلُونَ رِزۡقَكُمۡ أَنَّكُمۡ تُكَذِّبُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5061,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"56:83","price":"（你们）怎么不在灵魂到将死者的咽喉的时候--","arabic":"فَلَوۡلَآ إِذَا بَلَغَتِ ٱلۡحُلۡقُومَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5062,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"56:84","price":"那时候，你们大家看着他，","arabic":"وَأَنتُمۡ حِينَئِذٖ تَنظُرُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5063,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"56:85","price":"我比你们更临近他，但你们不晓得，","arabic":"وَنَحۡنُ أَقۡرَبُ إِلَيۡهِ مِنكُمۡ وَلَٰكِن لَّا تُبۡصِرُونَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5064,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"56:86","price":"如果你们不是受报应的，--","arabic":"فَلَوۡلَآ إِن كُنتُمۡ غَيۡرَ مَدِينِينَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5065,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"56:87","price":"你们怎不使灵魂复返于本位呢？如果你们是说实话的。","arabic":"تَرۡجِعُونَهَآ إِن كُنتُمۡ صَٰدِقِينَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5066,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"56:88","price":"如果他是被眷顾的，","arabic":"فَأَمَّآ إِن كَانَ مِنَ ٱلۡمُقَرَّبِينَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5067,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"56:89","price":"那么，他将享受舒适、给养与恩泽的乐园；","arabic":"فَرَوۡحٞ وَرَيۡحَانٞ وَجَنَّتُ نَعِيمٖ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5068,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"56:90","price":"如果他是幸福者，","arabic":"وَأَمَّآ إِن كَانَ مِنۡ أَصۡحَٰبِ ٱلۡيَمِينِ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5069,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"56:91","price":"那么，一般幸福的人将对他说：祝你平安！","arabic":"فَسَلَٰمٞ لَّكَ مِنۡ أَصۡحَٰبِ ٱلۡيَمِينِ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5070,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"56:92","price":"如果他是迷误的、否认复活者，","arabic":"وَأَمَّآ إِن كَانَ مِنَ ٱلۡمُكَذِّبِينَ ٱلضَّآلِّينَ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5071,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"56:93","price":"那么，他将享受沸水的款待，","arabic":"فَنُزُلٞ مِّنۡ حَمِيمٖ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5072,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"56:94","price":"和烈火的烧灼。","arabic":"وَتَصۡلِيَةُ جَحِيمٍ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5073,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"56:95","price":"这确是无可置疑的真理。","arabic":"إِنَّ هَٰذَا لَهُوَ حَقُّ ٱلۡيَقِينِ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5074,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"56:96","price":"故你应当颂扬你的主的大名。","arabic":"فَسَبِّحۡ بِٱسۡمِ رَبِّكَ ٱلۡعَظِيمِ","category":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah"],"ayahNumber":5075,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"}],"chapter":["56 (Al-Waqi'ah)","Al-Waqi'ah","Surah Al-Waqi'ah","Chapter Al-Waqi'ah","Waqi'ah","Surah Waqi'ah","Chapter Waqi'ah","Al Waqi'ah","Surah Al Waqi'ah","Chapter Al Waqi'ah","Surah 56","Chapter 56","The Inevitable","الواقعة"]}